<p>For general information about DUNS Numbers, please refer to Federal Acquisition Regulation (FAR) Clause 52.204-6, Data Universal Numbering System (DUNS) Number (10/2003) <br />https:/acquisition.gov/far/current/html/52_200_206.html</p><br />
